      <T n="text">0x5C16E453<!--Bring a little enchantment into your Sim's world with <font color="#199C2C"><b>Fairy Dust</b></font>! Fairy Dust is a magical substance that can be received directly from a Fairy or through <font color="#199C2C"><b>Foraging</b></font>. Fairies can also pick up a ration of Fairy Dust from the <font color="#199C2C"><b>Mossveil Fairy Hub</b></font> located in <font color="#199C2C"><b>Everdew</b></font> in <font color="#199C2C"><b>Innisgreen</b></font>. Fairies will drop Fairy Dust whenever they clean themselves or WooHoo/Mess Around with another Sim! They can also brush it off themselves which will create a pile in their inventory.\n\nFairy Dust has a variety of magical uses, such as:\n• Allowing Fairies to use the <font color="#199C2C"><b>Regenerate Emotional Force</b></font> Ability.\n• <font color="#199C2C"><b>Enchanting Plants</b></font>, which will make it so plants are fully watered as well as free of bugs and weeds! (See <font color="#199C2C"><b>Enchanted Gardening</b></font> Lesson)\n• Creating Enchanted objects with the <font color="#199C2C"><b>Nature Press</b></font>. (See <font color="#199C2C"><b>Nature Press</b></font> Lesson)\n• Bringing <font color="#199C2C"><b>Gnomes</b></font> to life to help with gardening, repairs, cleaning, or even protection from Death and Evil Gnomes.--></T>
